title: Kenn Bosak

Bosak makes crypto and NFTs more accessible to the general public. He’s been a Bitcoiner since 2015 and has now ventured into NFT territory. He has

his own website where he talks about NFTs, as well as a YouTube channel where he hosts videos of podcasts and NFTs.
